name: Ashley Swinford
text: It's always so convenient to call an order in and pop in to grab some pizzas. All the sides are tasty and the staff is always super friendly.

name: Todd Rider
text: They shorted my on my buffalo wings 9 in a 10 pc. Dangit

name: Patrick Shinkle
text: Excellent fast customized Personal Pan Pizza. And. I mean Excellent! Customer Service at this small Godfathers located in Oakland's Andy's Gas and Shop was personalized and exact.

name: William Schaffer
text: You can all most miss the  counter, it's in the back of the gas station store. The food is really  good  the chicken was made fresh and of course the pizza was made fresh too.
